=== 1999 : Juhadi Lḥusin ===
Aseggas umbeɛd, di 1999, yiwen uselmad umezruy Acelḥi n [[Ayt Baɛemran]] yudsen [[Sus]] di yiwet n tasnawit (Lycée) di tɣiwant n [[Anfa]] (Casablanca), di tmurt n Murakuc, Juhadi Elḥusin yga [http://www.freemorocco.com/tamkardit-library/El-quraan_s_Tamazight_al-qoraan_bi_al_amazighiya_Koran_in_Berber.pdf tasuqilt n Leqran akk] s 114 ixfawen-is, ar tutlayt Tamaziɣt seld mraw (10) iseggasen n leqdic ilmend n wannecta. Yura-t s-isekkilen n taɛrabt, aken i d-yenna, anecta ixedm-it i waken a t-yefhem yal Amaziɣ n [[Merruk]] mi ara t-iɣer.  

